text: Janet Andrewartha (16 September 1951 - 26 July 2024) was an Australian actress. She was known for her roles in Neighbours as Lyn Scully and in Prisoner as Rebecca "Reb" Kean. Andrewartha was born in Melbourne. Andrewartha died on 26 July 2024 in Melbourne at the age of 72. She was diagnosed with cancer three months before her death. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Australian movie actors Category:1951 births Category:2024 deaths Category:Australian television actors Category:Actors from Melbourne Category:Australian stage actors Category:Cancer deaths in Victoria (Australia)
